rows.label: tlk4234011304_msg0001
rows.name:
Toatoa is studying history
from salvaged items, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011304_msg0002
rows.name:
No one knows if salvaged items
were actually used in the way
their names suggest, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011304_msg0003
rows.name:
For example, the Fleet-in-a-Bottle has
a small model inside a bottle and is
said to be an ancient work of art, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011304_msg0004
rows.name:
It's a model of a ship similar in shape to
a Divine Beast ship, but... something like
this couldn't navigate the Cloud Sea, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011304_msg0005
rows.name:
It's too big for a boat on water,
too... So many mysteries, mo!
